name: Waldgeist
description:
Waldgeist, a mythical hybrid-creature of human and tree origin. It haunts and attacks souls with telekinesis that left known paths through sacred woods.

This is the 2nd piece of a series of moody digital mixed media artworks. The base is an iPhone SE (1 Gen) photography (ProCamera app) and a 3D Blender render of a model export from MagicaCSG/Nomad Sculpt. Retouch and post-processing made in Photoshop, SnapSeed, ProCamera and Procreate.
Resolution: 2928 x 3904 pxl, 264 dpi
